    <para><emphasis role="bold">Description:</emphasis> The permission mask of the file if it is created by syslog-ng. For octal numbers prefix the number with <userinput>0</userinput>, for example use <userinput>0755</userinput> for <userinput>rwxr-xr-x</userinput>.</para>
    <para>To preserve the original properties of an existing file, use the option without specifying an attribute: <parameter>perm()</parameter>.</para>
